Package: eid-mw
Section: libs
Replaces: libbeidlibopensc2, libbeidlib3
Conflicts: libbeidlibopensc2, libbeidlib3
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libccid, libacr38u
Description: low-level support for Belgian Electronic Identity Card
 This package contains a PKCS#11 module and a Firefox plugin for the
 Belgian electronic identity card. You should install it if you wish to
 use your electronic identity card to log on to online websites, or to
 sign your mail and documents with it.

Package: eid-viewer
Section: java
Provides: beidgui
Replaces: beidgui
Conflicts: beidgui
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, eid-mw
Description: Graphical interface to Belgian Electronic Identity Card
 This package contains a graphical application to read data from the
 Belgian electronic identity card.
